{"tid":845724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小米被美企控侵權　股價新低","createTime":"2018-10-03T01:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T03:14:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"57915e38c3721791dce3a81f6ef7424a0a8d7782","tid":845724,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:33:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20181003/20513678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181003%2F20513678&d=vafsAJtW1FASTd9W%2FbGZwpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7424fbe9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181003%2F20513678&h=f4d79dcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20181003/20513678</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月03日 <br />\n<br />\n小米被美企控侵權　股價新低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181003/large/03bl33p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181003%2Flarge%2F03bl33p.jpg&h=ea6d0c20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小米近年面對多宗侵權訴訟。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】早前被美國技術公司控告侵權的小米（1810），昨股價顯著下挫，最低曾見14.8元，收報15元，連續五個交易日下跌，創上市後新低，並較招股價17元下跌逾一成。<br />\n<br />\n早前內地傳媒《國際金融報》報道，一間名為Dareltech的美國技術公司在美國紐約南區聯邦法院，起訴小米「故意、肆無忌憚地蓄意侵犯」（willfully, wantonly and deliberately infringing）四項專利，法院公開訊息顯示，起訴的原因是「專利侵權」，涉及周邊設備，包括小米自拍桿。<br />\n<br />\n訴狀指，Dareltech曾在今年8月27日以信件通知小米其侵權行為，在9月12日的信中，小米承認Dareltech公司的信件，但卻表示「小米不需要取得Dareltech的專利授權」。訴狀提到，小米早已得悉及承認了其侵權行為，認為小米是蓄意且有意識地侵犯專利，故要求小米3倍的損害賠償金。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n訴訟已在美立案<br />\n<br />\n小米在香港上市時曾表示，會持續與美國電訊業者洽談，料明年將有機會進入美國市場，但之後創辦人雷軍就指，目前國際市場發展太快，暫不進入美國市場。現時小米美國官網以售賣小量電子配件為主，惟未見有自拍桿。<br />\n<br />\n訴訟已於上周一（9月24日）在紐約南區聯邦法院立案，更已指定了法官，並於上周五（9月28日）通知美國專利商標局局長。小米集團負責人對事件不予置評。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\nWebb：證監凍結戶口料屬藍鼎<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n亞馬遜最低工資增至每小時$117"},{"pid":"78f5a29199b5b515be865ccca4b3004d7542cfc0","tid":845724,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:34:12.000Z","msg":"垃圾股"},{"pid":"57e01aea25e28633b2029a2d1dcebe3bf91de64e","tid":845724,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:51:23.000Z","msg":"到而家先有人告佢咪偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成間公司有咩唔係抄人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2d8866141ccb4587e4a4f11d6baf86cf4f9fd7","tid":845724,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:55:11.000Z","msg":"美國一早睇定你入門口就放你血"},{"pid":"82565e4fd4cab47dce8400c5fab791ba154e5888","tid":845724,"uid":186087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:16:56.000Z","msg":"佢有冇問過自己良心, 有咩係原創, 先好上市la"},{"pid":"e198e00d6fecb3dcfe6771dfef1128bbe945e35d","tid":845724,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:04:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee4533701ba534fed2fe55e86c8ea37e2a4a41d","tid":845724,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82565e4fd4cab47dce8400c5fab791ba154e5888","tid":845724,"uid":186087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:16:56.000Z","msg":"佢有冇問過自己良心, 有咩係原創, 先好上市la"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:10:39.000Z","msg":"要問昆蟲學專家先知"},{"pid":"97393fa0b60129a2d6d4565a8df652b383f47008","tid":845724,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:14:03.000Z","msg":"之前睇過啲文,話支那公司特登去外國然後畀人告,賠天文數字,其實係自己告自己,走資嘅一種方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}